{"id": 2233, "genre": 1001, "title": "让你念念不忘的情景喜剧都有啥特别的？", "description": "《老友记》《我爱我家》《武林外传》……你的“没事就想重温”列表里都有谁？（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 3093, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180319135303R3bZItfd0DlWnHxu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-20T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 271618, "content": "我爱我家，是不是暴露年龄了？好吧，我爱我爱我家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977871}, {"id": 271619, "content": "Legal High", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920529}, {"id": 271875, "content": "我爱我家，武林外传百看不腻，演员，剧情，台词，洋洋好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034688}, {"id": 271620, "content": "看着武林外传长大", "image": "img/option/option/20180320160646xUTVHZMrlIjyQ7cs", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290977}, {"id": 271876, "content": "老友们永远欢聚，最晦暗时候一定要看老友记", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148578}, {"id": 272388, "content": "外来媳妇本地郎 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291592}, {"id": 271622, "content": "生活大爆炸，一直在追，每个人的性格分明，而又特别的默契。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290721}, {"id": 271878, "content": "武林外传！所有的都下载了！看三遍了！看不腻啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289092}, {"id": 273671, "content": "东北一家人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 271624, "content": "武林外传三观正的不行，建议九年制义务教育强制观看，公务员、事业人员每月集中学习并撰写观影心得。", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291089}, {"id": 272648, "content": "爱情公寓，永远不忘的青葱岁月", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271239}, {"id": 273160, "content": "看起来没负担，很轻松。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297980}, {"id": 271625, "content": "一定是爱情公寓，把我从美剧的泥潭中拯救出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 699486}, {"id": 271628, "content": "爱情公寓，曾小贤的眉毛舞，卷纸舞，一菲的霸气外露，凌晨三点半的子乔的女装，美嘉的如来神掌，关谷的谜之推理，成语解读，悠悠的唐氏演技", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1152946}, {"id": 271629, "content": "武林外传，爱情公寓，家有儿女。温暖是永久的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714055}, {"id": 272397, "content": "周星驰的所有电影系列", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141832}, {"id": 271630, "content": "个人感觉废柴联盟比TBBT更有趣味：枕头大战、床单大战、水枪大战、像素大战等等太有意思了。女主们演技到位不生硬，妖而不露，十分可人。各种梗各种包袱自然而有内涵，能够让人产生会心一笑的感觉。然而该剧已然狗带，没能带出一个强硬的IP。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291089}, {"id": 271886, "content": "成长的烦恼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036007}, {"id": 271631, "content": "爱情公寓", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253414}, {"id": 271633, "content": "发现好多喜欢爱情公寓的，话说爱情公寓抄袭老友记太严重了，我都看不下去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104124}, {"id": 272657, "content": "炊事班的故事和东北一家人，轻易不敢点开一集，只要点开一集必须得整部剧循环一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895976}, {"id": 271634, "content": "最经典的《老友记》", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526909}, {"id": 271635, "content": "士兵突击吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289005}, {"id": 271638, "content": "难道不是基友都住在一起，爱的人都住在隔壁么", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337493}, {"id": 272662, "content": "家有外星人\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294902}, {"id": 282134, "content": "《神烦警探》根本停不下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346129}, {"id": 271639, "content": "我一个95后，钟情《父母爱情》。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1279875}, {"id": 272663, "content": "外来媳妇本地郎\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1294902}, {"id": 271641, "content": "搞笑一家人啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475929}, {"id": 271642, "content": "卓别林式的喜剧，不仅幽默还极具讽刺……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291130}, {"id": 271643, "content": "绝对是《武林外传》，它做得好的，是现在剧都缺的，就是内容。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291129}, {"id": 271644, "content": "老友记，现在都在看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236472}, {"id": 271646, "content": "地下交通站。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291148}, {"id": 271647, "content": "法国短片【简而言之】，特逗又戳心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189259}, {"id": 272928, "content": "《生活大爆炸》，和高智商的人对话很困难！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296758}, {"id": 271649, "content": "了不起的麦瑟尔夫人", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290741}, {"id": 273185, "content": "地下交通站?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298010}, {"id": 271650, "content": "家有儿女算吗。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291167}, {"id": 271651, "content": "绝对的爱情公寓和生活大爆炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1276711}, {"id": 271653, "content": "it狂人，就这么完结了好可惜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291157}, {"id": 271655, "content": "武林外传 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1288801}, {"id": 271656, "content": "家有儿女，是一部陪伴了我的童年的家庭喜剧。剧里的欢笑、悲伤都十分符合生活中的点滴，让我的心为之感动?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123397}, {"id": 271657, "content": "《百年酒馆》\n怎一个丧字了得啊\n唉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163742}, {"id": 271659, "content": "broke girls", "image": "img/option/option/2018032017575483UzuvOCQ1GV7kJW", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241445}, {"id": 271915, "content": "费城永远阳光灿烂\n工作狂workaholics\n我爱上的人是奇葩\n超级超市 superstore\n儿童医院children hospital", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008226}, {"id": 271660, "content": "只有我看《犯罪心理》么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066413}, {"id": 271661, "content": "必须武林外传！！！老少皆宜，内容健康，积极向上，永垂不朽！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227589}, {"id": 271662, "content": "情深深雨濛濛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286490}, {"id": 272942, "content": "武林外传", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039533}, {"id": 272943, "content": "前一段时间狂刷地下交通站", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039533}]}